AUDIO: 'to you. Turn uh turning underused assets into automatic dividends requires clear channels or pipes that move cash flow to citizens without heavy bureaucracy. This is one of the primary things is we want to get the government out of the way as'

[00:53] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'much as possible. So many of these are market-based and private property based solutions. However, in some cases we will need government intervention to help out. Um which I know that some people are are allergic to that. But you also have to consider that you know'

